strings:
<voice_0x0100158B><se_def>*: Ah, thank you.
You saved us from disaster.

<voice_0x0100158C><se_high>*: But what are we going to do?
If Cash and Carrie hear about this...
<voice_0x0100158D><se_def>*: ...We'll have to make sure it never gets out.

<voice_0x0100158E><se_low>*: It's gone too far now.
We'll have to shut them up.

<voice_0x0100158F><se_high>*: Yes, we'll have to...
buy them off with...tokens!

<voice_0x01001590><se_high>*: Please! We'll give you 200 tokens if you promise not to tell Cash and Carrie about
any of this.

<voice_0x01001591><se_high>*: Are you trying to get more out of me!?
I can offer you 400, but that's it! No more!

<voice_0x01001592><se_high>*: I said I wouldn't give you any more.
400 tokens is my last offer!
<voice_0x01001593><se_high>*: Thank you! I'll have the tokens credited to your account.

<voice_0x01001594><se_def>*: Then it's a promise!
Not a word of this to anyone!
